Interface KbTerm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    KbObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface KbTerm

    • Method Detail

      • provablyNotInstanceOf

        boolean provablyNotInstanceOf(KbCollection col,
                            Context ctx)
        Determine whether this is provably not an instance of col. This means that there is no way to convert this into an instance of col without editing or removing current KB assertions.
        Parameters:
        col - the collection which this is to be tested against
        ctx - the context in which the semantic test should be performed
        Returns:
        whether this is provably not an instance of col

      • provablyNotInstanceOf

        boolean provablyNotInstanceOf(String colStr,
                            String ctxStr)
        Determine whether this is provably not an instance of col. This means that there is no way to convert this into an instance of the collection without editing or removing current KB assertions.
        Parameters:
        colStr - the string representing the collection which this is to be tested against
        ctxStr - the context in which the semantic test should be performed
        Returns:
        whether this is provably not an instance col

      • getCreator

        KbIndividual getCreator()
        Return the #$Cyclist (not necessarily #$HumanCyclist) who created this term. If not found or if there is an exception, return null.
        Returns:
        the cyclist who created the term

      • getCreationDate
